==Introduction==
The '''Static Content''' widget allows to display any arbitrary content defined using MediaWiki syntax.

In most cases it is used to display just a static text and images.


==Definition==
<pre>
<concept name="{CONCEPT}">
  <structure>
    ...
    <staticContent name="{NAME}" label="{LABEL}"/>
      <text>{CONTENT}</text>
    </staticContent>
    ...
  </structure>
</concept>
</pre>

{| class="helptable"
|-
! {CONCEPT}
| A name of the Concept.
|-
! {NAME}
| A name of the Static Content widget.
|-
! {LABEL}
| A label of the Static Content widget, if not set the {NAME} is used as a label.
|-
! {CONTENT}
| The content to be displayed on the page.
|}



==Example==
<pre>
<concept name="Event">
  <structure>
    <staticContent name="Title">
      <text>
Any text content [[File:Any image.png]] ..
'''Some bold content''' ... and ''italic''
      </text>
    </staticContent>
  </structure>
</concept>
</pre>


==User Interface==
The content of the "Static Content" widget is displayed on View and Edit Pages.
